card.name: Blastoise
card.description: It crushes its foe under its heavy body to cause fainting. In a pinch, it will withdraw inside its shell.

card.name: Great Ball
card.description: Look at the top 7 cards of your deck. You may reveal a Pokémon you find there and put it into your hand. Shuffle the other cards back into your deck.

card.name: Pikachu
card.description: Its nature is to store up electricity. Forests where nests of Pikachu live are dangerous, since the trees are so often struck by lightning.
